    "summary": "The user expresses deep feelings of inadequacy and toxic parentage, suggesting that their death might be the best thing for their children. The assistant repeatedly validates the user's pain and provides empathetic responses, but it consistently directs the user toward professional help and mental health resources while resisting any validation of the user's suicidal ideation as a solution.",
